Atlas Copco may go into new areas - new CEO . The new head of Swedish industrial engineer Atlas Copco , Giulio Mazzalupi , said on Monday the company may launch into new operational areas . " You can work in many dimensions to increase growth and other areas are a possible dimension , " Mazzalupi told a press conference , after being named as the company ' s new chief executive to replace Michael Treschow . " We have a good platform to increase growth . " It is important that I will ensure that all plans and strategies continue unchanged until this is carried through . " Mazzalupi will take the helm of Atlas Copco at the end of April when Treschow moves to head appliance maker Electrolux . - - Stockholm newsroom + 46 - 8 - 700 1017 
